item.title: From Data Analyst to Leadership in Tech
item.description: Introduction: Hello , and welcome to my blog! My name is Isagani Jaen, and I’m excited to share my journey with you. Through this blog, I aim to provide insights into my professional experiences, lessons learned, and expertise in the tech industry. My Professional Journey: My journey in the tech world began on June 2012. Over the years, I’ve had the opportunity to work with some incredible teams and tackle a variety of projects that have shaped my skills and perspective.

Experience Software Development Senior Analyst Accenture in the Philippines Jun 2022 - Present 路 Worked directly with clients as GNR-Analytics Lead. 路 Applied innovative ideas to drive the automation of Delivery Analytics at the client level using technologies such as clients' internal Business Intelligence Suite, Google's F1 Engine, Google SQL, Workflow Pipeline, Google App Scripts and performed data analysis using Python and Colab. System Developer Analyst Accenture in the Philippines Oct 2020 - Jun 2022 路 1 yr 9 mos 路 Perfromed ETL, reports mobilization, dashboard creation, workflow automation, and reporting automation.
